Description: This package implements tools for quantitative research
    in scientometrics and bibliometrics. It provides routines for importing
    bibliographic data from Thomson Reuters' Web of Science (<http://
    www.webofknowledge.com>) and performing bibliometric analysis.
    For more information visit 
    <https://rubenfcasal.github.io/scimetr/articles/scimetr.html>.
